// loop.fsb — fasb while-loop construct (NEW word-based syntax).
// Syntax: while <metric> <op> <n> do cmd1 ; cmd2 ; ...
//   op:     != > >= < <=
//   metric: #facets (= 2 * facets.len()), #route (route length)
// Walks the navigation tree: take a step while #facets > 5, show facets each iteration.
while #facets > 5 do step ; facets
route
count
solvecount
:q
